sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from "react" import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom" import { MDBContainer, MDBNavbar, MDBNavbarBrand, MDBNavbarToggler, MDBIcon, MDBNavbarNav, MDBNavbarItem, MDBCollapse, } from "mdb-react-ui-kit" export default function Navbar({ routeItems }) { const [showNavSecond, setShowNavSecond] = useState(false) return ( setShowNavSecond(!showNavSecond)} > {routeItems.map((navItem, index) => ( {navItem.text} ))} {/* Home Games */} ) }
